No. 09-1063 (R46-016). David W. Corbitt, et al., Petitioners v. Home Depot USA, Inc. 560 U.S. 920, 130 S. Ct. 3318,

176 L. Ed. 2d 1215,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 4159. May 20, 2010.

The petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eleventh Circuit in the above-entitled case was dismissed today pursuant to this Court’s Rule 46.

Same case below, 589 F.3d 1136.
